5-28-55.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1663651735670&amp;api=3Dv2" =
data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1202995173" =
data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment"=
 data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image2022-9-20_15-28-55.png" data-ba=
se-url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au" data-linked-resource-conte=
nt-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1203279605" data=
-linked-resource-container-version=3D"4" alt=3D"" width=3D"468"></span></p>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"RolesandResponsibilties-YourroleasaWestpacMeshDeveloper"><strong>=
Your role as a Westpac Mesh Developer&nbsp;</strong></h2>
<p>The Designer will provide the Developer with the component contract whic=
h defines your API.</p>
<p>The Developer implements the contract by writing the code logic.</p>
<p>The Developer writes the unit tests and integration (idempotent) test ca=
ses and ensures they pass.</p>
<p>The Developer manages deployments to the platform, and performs PIV.</p>
<p>The Developer is responsible for managing security reviews with ISG.</p>
<p>The Developer is responsible for maintaining, supporting and troubleshoo=
ting their component.</p>
<p>Westpac Mesh is a platform to make it easier to build and run digital so=
lutions. You still own your API</p>
<p><br></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<p><br></p>
</div><strong style=3D"text-decoration: underline" class=3D"pageTitle" data=
-content-id=3D"1203279607">Swagger Specification</strong>
<div class=3D"tabs-pane active-pane" id=3D"a754afe0-7384-4b32-acf3-e4bd6c8d=
0746-1203279607">
<div class=3D"sectionColumnWrapper">
<div class=3D"sectionMacro">
<div class=3D"sectionMacroRow">
<div class=3D"columnMacro">
<h2 id=3D"SwaggerSpecification-HowwelldoyouknowSwagger?"><strong>How well d=
o you know </strong><strong>Swagger</strong><strong>?</strong></h2>
<ul>
<li>Swagger is the industry standard specification for RESTful webservices<=
/li>
<li>Forces contract-first development, we encourage project teams to genera=
te code from their Swagger specification</li>
<li>Westpac Mesh provides a pre-defined 'Golden template':&nbsp;<a href=3D"=
https://bitbucket.srv.westpac.com.au/projects/WDP2/repos/contracts/browse/t=
emplates" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://bitbucket.srv.we=
stpac.com.au/projects/WDP2/repos/contracts/browse/templates</a>&nbsp;</li>
<li>Consumable by all Westpac Mesh customers</li>
<li>The Swagger specification goes through a governance process and has to =
be digitally signed before deployment to higher environments</li>
</ul>
<h2 id=3D"SwaggerSpecification-HowdoweuseSwaggerfromday1?"><strong>How do w=
e use </strong><strong>Swagger</strong><strong> from day 1?</strong></h2>
<p>We can simultaneously:</p>
<ul>
<li>Code</li>
<li>Test</li>
<li>Consume</li>
</ul>
<h2 id=3D"SwaggerSpecification-MoreInformation"><strong>More Information</s=
trong></h2>
<p>More in-depth details for writing a Swagger specification and design sta=
ndards are given in the Westpac Mesh Designer Induction (search 'Mesh' in e=
Academy).</p>
<p>Westpac Mesh hosts a Swagger editor to allow you to easily edit a Swagge=
r:&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://swagger.mesh.westpac.com.au/" class=3D"external-=
link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://swagger.mesh.westpac.com.au/</a></p>
<p>Click the below link to get more general information on the Swagger webs=
ite.</p>
<p><a href=3D"https://swagger.io/" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow"=
><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual=
-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image confluence-thumbnail" dragga=
ble=3D"false" height=3D"100" src=3D"dd5de5f9aba344ae12bad1682fbc60f6ea2b4d8=
a7f8bfc3ebda94ce016a035a7" data-image-src=3D"/download/attachments/12032796=
