<h2 id=3D"MeshConnect-ExploringourMarketplace"><strong>Exploring our Market=
place</strong></h2>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">Mesh Connect is our service portal fo=
r Westpac Staff to navigate WDP/Mesh. Mesh Connect is a one-stop shop for e=
ngagement, on-boarding and management of Components hosted on the Platform.=
&nbsp;</span></p>
<p>From Mesh Connect you can:&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<ul>
<li>Browse Components:=20
<ul>
<li>View by Deployments</li>
</ul></li>
<li>View Ownership Details of Components (Domain and Architecture)</li>
<li>Create and Search Mesh Engagements</li>
<li>Find useful Tools and Guides</li>
<li>Get links to Training Material</li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">Head to <a href=3D"https://me=
sh.westpac.com.au/" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">Mesh Connect</=
a> now and check it out for yourself!</span></strong></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manu=
