<p></p>
<div class=3D"">
<div class=3D"childtabs-macro" data-fixed-position=3D"false">
<div class=3D"aui-tabs horizontal-tabs" data-aui-responsive=3D"true">
<strong style=3D"text-decoration: underline" class=3D"pageTitle" data-conte=
nt-id=3D"1300588564">Westpac Mesh Chapters &amp; Guilds</strong>
<div class=3D"tabs-pane active-pane" id=3D"9e67b5d5-2bee-4834-b47a-2fa37844=
733b-1300588564">
<p><span><span class=3D"TextRun SCXW176427353 BCX0" style=3D"color: rgb(0,0=
,0);"><span class=3D"NormalTextRun SCXW176427353 BCX0">In the agile communi=
ty, some may also know of Spotify's use of chapters and guilds, and this mo=
del was re-explored in WDP.</span></span></span></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"relative-table confluenceTable" style=3D"width: 1266.03px;"=
>
