0-1004478_community-cartoon.png"></span></span></p>
</div></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><h2 id=
=3D"WestpacMeshChapters&amp;Guilds-Background"><strong>Background</strong><=
/h2><p><span>Let's start with a history of guilds as its quite a powerful i=
nsight.</span><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span>There was craft guilds and co=
vered market guilds - the latter were strong powerbases. In Italy they foug=
ht over control of the government.</span><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span>In=
 more recent times, we have examples in Australia such as</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span>Australian Computer Society &amp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>=
privacy law lobbying</span></li>
<li><span>Master&nbsp;</span><span>B</span><span>uilder Association, claddi=
ng issues and training certification</span></li>
</ul><p>Chapters and Guilds are for discussions about what is right thing t=
o do.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><br></p>
</div><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper =
