<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<h2 id=3D"WestpacMeshChapters&amp;Guilds-Chapters"><strong>Chapters</strong=
></h2>
<p>The chapter is a small group of people having similar skills and working=
 within the same general competency area, with the same train.</p>
<p>Each Chapter has a chapter lead who is responsible for enabling the team=
 members to perform their role and is accountable for the quality.</p>
<p>The design chapter lead group meets fortnightly, which layers over the s=
wagger governance meetings that happen twice a week.</p>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper con=
fluence-embedded-manual-size"><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapp=
er image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"conf=
luence-embedded-image image-center" draggable=3D"false" width=3D"350" src=
