</div><strong style=3D"text-decoration: underline" class=3D"pageTitle" data=
-content-id=3D"1300588625">The Ask</strong>
<div class=3D"tabs-pane active-pane" id=3D"9e67b5d5-2bee-4834-b47a-2fa37844=
733b-1300588625">
<h2 style=3D"" id=3D"TheAsk-Peoplehelpingpeople"><strong>People helping peo=
ple</strong></h2>
<p style=3D""><br></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col>
<col>
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manu=
al-size"><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedde=
d-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image confluence-thumbnail=
" draggable=3D"false" width=3D"100" src=3D"978445f209f24d234b6cac427abb3f5e=
debc4de1874cd990ba8983d6ce8e5fbd" data-image-src=3D"/download/attachments/1=
300588625/Picture8.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1674624259293&amp=
;api=3Dv2" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1=
300588621" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"=
attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"Picture8.png" data-base-u=
rl=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au" data-linked-resource-content-t=
ype=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1300588625" data-lin=
ked-resource-container-version=3D"1" alt=3D"" height=3D"101"></span></span>=
</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<h3 id=3D"TheAsk-Futurereadymindset">Future ready mindset</h3>
<p>Being willing to change and grow, to learn through failing, to challenge=
 the why and how and not fall back into previous practices is part of the f=
uture ready mindset.</p>
<p>In a past world where delivery was done in stages with handoffs between =
teams, it is key to think about trying new possibilities. With much shorter=
 turnaround times for NONPROD and PROD CRQs (1 and 3 days respectively), an=
d a typical deploy time of ~17 minutes, and open access to logs through Spl=
unk, this lack of friction makes handoffs between teams a significant loss =
of time.</p>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper con=
fluence-embedded-manual-size"><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapp=
er image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"conf=
luence-embedded-image confluence-thumbnail image-center" draggable=3D"false=
" width=3D"80" src=3D"33e54e8d3bfc6c5eb3491e9f1ee09ffd805358f351ca358bdf41b=
2fc34db7e0e" data-image-src=3D"/download/attachments/1300588625/Picture9.pn=
g?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1674624259230&amp;api=3Dv2" data-unres=
olved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1300588622" data-linke=
d-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-link=
ed-resource-default-alias=3D"Picture9.png" data-base-url=3D"https://conflue=
nce.srv.westpac.com.au" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" dat=
a-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1300588625" data-linked-resource-containe=
r-version=3D"1" alt=3D"" height=3D"83"></span></span></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<h3 id=3D"TheAsk-Committoupskill">Commit to upskill</h3>
<p>Levelling up skills is to be expected, so plan to accommodate this. Whet=
her it's learning Postman, or becoming fluent with the UI framework, or sim=
ply keeping up with the latest features, learning new skills is a must-do. =
A recent engagement for consuming an existing API said that, once they got =
through the initial learning curve, that this was a 'cake walk'. It's worth=
 getting through the learning needed.</p>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manu=
al-size"><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedde=
d-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image confluence-thumbnail=
