inked-resource-container-version=3D"1" alt=3D"" height=3D"100"></span></spa=
n></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<h3 id=3D"TheAsk-IdentifyyourChapterLeadsandchampions">Identify your Chapte=
r Leads and champions</h3>
<p>Identifying Chapter Leads in your part of the ecosystem is fundamental t=
o fast-tracking your way through governance.</p>
</div></td>
</tr>
