<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<h3 id=3D"TheAsk-Beproactiveinthecommunityandguilds">Be proactive in the co=
mmunity and guilds</h3>
<p>Being proactive is a call to be brave and have courage. There is an oppo=
rtunity to learn beyond your current role, and be valued in the community -=
 whether it's showing support for questions, or being the one raising or an=
swering questions.</p>
