onasinboundsecurity">Scenario 3.1.4 : Partner proxy that requires JWT Valid=
ation(using static JWK) from X-Authorization Header and Basic Authenticatio=
n as inbound security</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenario3.1.5:Partnerproxythatrequire=
sJWTValidation(usingstaticJWK)fromX-AuthorizationHeaderthroughtheSIMPLIFIED=
PARTNERGATEWAY(OAuth2+TLSonly)">Scenario 3.1.5 : Partner proxy that require=
s JWT Validation(using static JWK) from X-Authorization Header through the =
SIMPLIFIED PARTNER GATEWAY (OAuth 2 + TLS only)</a></li>
</ul></li>
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-2.WSDLProxies">2. WSDL Proxies</a>
<ul class=3D"toc-indentation">
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenario3.2.1:PartnerWSDLproxythatreq=
uiresPasswordDigest(UNT)asinboundsecurity">Scenario 3.2.1 : Partner WSDL pr=
oxy that requires Password Digest (UNT) as inbound security</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenatio3.2.2:PartnerWSDLproxythatreq=
uiredPasswordCleartext(UNT)asinboundsecurity">Scenatio 3.2.2 : Partner WSDL=
 proxy that required Password Cleartext (UNT) as inbound security</a></li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-4.ExternalCustomerGateway">4. Externa=
l Customer Gateway</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-5.ExternalProspectGateway">5. Externa=
l Prospect Gateway</a></li>
