(UNT)alongwithSSLasoutboundsecurity(UNTCleartext&amp;TLS)">Scenario&nbsp;1.=
2.4 : Web Service Proxy invoking a web service that require Password Cleart=
ext (UNT) as Inbound Security and Cleartext Password(UNT) along with SSL as=
 outbound security (UNT Cleartext&nbsp;&amp; TLS)</h3>
<p>Endpoint is&nbsp;'<a rel=3D"nofollow">https://providerurl:50270'</a>&nbs=
p;and base path is /provider/base/path will need the TLS using Westpac Root=
 CA public cert. Also the web service need to connect to provider using Use=
rname Token (Password Digest) username as 'test_username' and password is '=
test_password'.</p>
