<h1 id=3D"Proxyusecasescenarios-2.ExternalStaffGateway">2. External Staff G=
ateway</h1>
<p>For all Staff Experience APIs you should configure the user community in=
 the component.yaml file to include staff. This will automatically apply th=
e staff NIDP JWT Authentication policy to your API.</p>
<h1 id=3D"Proxyusecasescenarios-3.ExternalPartnerGateway">3. External Partn=
er Gateway</h1>
<h2 id=3D"Proxyusecasescenarios-1.APIProxies">1.&nbsp;API Proxies</h2>
<h3 id=3D"Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenario3.1.1:Partnerproxythatrequiresbasic=
authenticationasinboundsecurity">Scenario&nbsp;3.1.1 : Partner proxy that r=
equires basic authentication as inbound security</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;"><b>env/default/proxy.yaml</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">---=20
backendService:
 basePath: /provider/base/path
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h3 id=3D"Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenario3.1.2:PartnerproxythatrequiresJWTVa=
lidationasinboundsecurityusingPINGIDP(staticJWKininventory)">Scenario&nbsp;=
3.1.2 : Partner proxy that requires&nbsp;JWT Validation as inbound security=
 using PING IDP (static JWK in inventory)</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;"><b>env/default/proxy.yaml</b>
</div>
