<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">---=20
backendService:
 basePath: /provider/base/path
inboundSecurityPolicy: INBOUND_AUTH_PARTNER_PING_JWT_VALIDATION_V1.0
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h3 id=3D"Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenario3.1.3:PartnerproxythatrequiresJWTVa=
lidationasinboundsecurityusingEAMIDP(staticJWKininventory)">Scenario&nbsp;3=
.1.3 : Partner proxy that requires JWT Validation as inbound security using=
